  </div>
  <div class="vocab-grid" id="vocab-container"></div>
</div>

<!-- PLURALS -->
<div id="plurals" class="section">
  <div class="page-title">Pluriels irréguliers 🔤</div>
  <div class="lesson-card"><div class="lesson-title">📖 Les pluriels sans S</div>
    <table class="rule-table">
      <tr><th>Singulier</th><th>Pluriel</th><th>Traduction</th></tr>
      <tr><td>child</td><td><strong>children</strong></td><td>enfant / enfants</td></tr>
      <tr><td>man</td><td><strong>men</strong></td><td>homme / hommes</td></tr>
      <tr><td>woman</td><td><strong>women</strong></td><td>femme / femmes</td></tr>
      <tr><td>person</td><td><strong>people</strong></td><td>personne / personnes</td></tr>
      <tr><td>tooth</td><td><strong>teeth</strong></td><td>dent / dents</td></tr>
      <tr><td>foot</td><td><strong>feet</strong></td><td>pied / pieds</td></tr>
      <tr><td>mouse</td><td><strong>mice</strong></td><td>souris</td></tr>
      <tr><td>goose</td><td><strong>geese</strong></td><td>oie / oies</td></tr>
      <tr><td>sheep</td><td><strong>sheep</strong></td><td>mouton(s)</td></tr>
      <tr><td>fish</td><td><strong>fish</strong></td><td>poisson(s)</td></tr>
    </table>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- IDIOMS -->
<div id="idioms" class="section">
  <div class="page-title">Expressions idiomatiques 🗣️</div>
  <div class="lesson-card"><div class="lesson-title">💬 Expressions du quotidien</div>
    <table class="rule-table">
      <tr><th>Expression</th><th>Sens littéral</th><th>Vrai sens</th></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>Break a leg!</strong></td><td>Casse-toi une jambe !</td><td>Bonne chance !</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>It's raining cats and dogs.</strong></td><td>Il pleut des chats et des chiens.</td><td>Il pleut des cordes.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>Under the weather.</strong></td><td>Sous la météo.</td><td>Ne pas se sentir bien.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>Bite the bullet.</strong></td><td>Mordre la balle.</td><td>Serrer les dents.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>Spill the beans.</strong></td><td>Renverser les haricots.</td><td>Vendre la mèche.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>Cost an arm and a leg.</strong></td><td>Coûter un bras et une jambe.</td><td>Coûter les yeux de la tête.</td></tr>
    </table>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- PHONETICS -->
<div id="phonetics" class="section">
  <div class="page-title">Phonétique 🎵</div>
  <div class="lesson-card"><div class="lesson-title">📖 Sons difficiles & mots pièges</div>
    <table class="rule-table">
      <tr><th>Mot</th><th>Prononciation</th><th>Traduction</th></tr>
      <tr><td>Honest</td><td>ON-est (H muet !)</td><td>Honnête</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Wednesday</td><td>WENZ-day</td><td>Mercredi</td></tr>
      <tr><td>February</td><td>FEB-roo-ery</td><td>Février</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Comfortable</td><td>COMF-ter-ble</td><td>Confortable</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Entrepreneur</td><td>on-truh-pruh-NUR</td><td>Entrepreneur</td></tr>
    </table>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- MUSIC -->
<div id="music" class="section">
  <div class="page-title">🎵 Apprendre avec la musique</div>
  <div class="page-sub">Chaque chanson t'apprend la grammaire — ligne par ligne !</div>
  <div class="music-box">🎵 Pour respecter le droit d'auteur, j'analyse la grammaire et le style avec des exemples inspirés de ces chansons. Pour les paroles complètes → Genius.com</div>

  <div class="music-card">
    <div class="music-header"><div class="music-emoji">🎤</div><div><div class="music-title">Die With A Smile</div><div class="music-artist">Bruno Mars & Lady Gaga</div></div></div>
    <div class="music-body">
      <div class="lyric-line highlight"><div class="lyric-en">"I don't wanna be without you"</div><div class="lyric-fr">Je ne veux pas être sans toi</div><span class="lyric-explain">💜 "don't wanna" = don't want to (familier)</span><span class="lyric-grammar">📖 DON'T + verbe = négation présent</span></div>
      <div class="lyric-line"><div class="lyric-en">"You're the reason I'm still breathing"</div><div class="lyric-fr">Tu es la raison pour laquelle je respire encore</div><span class="lyric-explain">💜 "you're" = you are (contraction)</span><span class="lyric-grammar">📖 ARE + -ING = action en cours</span></div>
      <div class="lyric-line highlight"><div class="lyric-en">"I would die for you, my darling"</div><div class="lyric-fr">Je mourrais pour toi, mon chéri/ma chérie</div><span class="lyric-explain">💜 WOULD = conditionnel</span><span class="lyric-grammar">📖 MY = possessif</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="music-card">
    <div class="music-header"><div class="music-emoji">🎤</div><div><div class="music-title">Sorry</div><div class="music-artist">Justin Bieber</div></div></div>
    <div class="music-body">
      <div class="lyric-line highlight"><div class="lyric-en">"Is it too late now to say sorry?"</div><div class="lyric-fr">Est-il trop tard maintenant pour dire pardon ?</div><span class="lyric-explain">💜 Question rhétorique</span><span class="lyric-grammar">📖 IS IT = question avec être | TOO + adj = trop</span></div>
      <div class="lyric-line"><div class="lyric-en">"I'm not trying to hurt you"</div><div class="lyric-fr">Je n'essaie pas de te blesser</div><span class="lyric-explain">💜 Défense — il explique ses intentions</span><span class="lyric-grammar">📖 I'M NOT = négation | TRYING = -ING</span></div>
      <div class="lyric-line highlight"><div class="lyric-en">"Will you forgive me?"</div><div class="lyric-fr">Est-ce que tu me pardonneras ?</div><span class="lyric-explain">💜 Question au futur</span><span class="lyric-grammar">📖 WILL + sujet = question futur</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="music-card">
    <div class="music-header"><div class="music-emoji">🎸</div><div><div class="music-title">Starlight</div><div class="music-artist">Muse</div></div></div>
    <div class="music-body">
      <div class="lyric-line highlight"><div class="lyric-en">"I just wanted to hold you in my arms"</div><div class="lyric-fr">Je voulais juste te tenir dans mes bras</div><span class="lyric-explain">💜 Désir passé</span><span class="lyric-grammar">📖 WANTED = passé | IN MY ARMS = préposition IN</span></div>
      <div class="lyric-line"><div class="lyric-en">"I'll never let you go"</div><div class="lyric-fr">Je ne te laisserai jamais partir</div><span class="lyric-explain">💜 Promesse forte</span><span class="lyric-grammar">📖 I'LL = I WILL | NEVER = jamais</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

