  <div class="lesson-card"><div class="lesson-title">📖 La méthode</div>
    <div class="example"><div class="en">✅ She <strong>works</strong> every day.</div><div class="fr">Affirmatif</div></div>
    <div class="example"><div class="en">❌ She <strong>doesn't work</strong> every day.</div><div class="fr">Négatif → ajoute DOESN'T, enlève le S</div></div>
    <div class="example"><div class="en">❓ <strong>Does</strong> she <strong>work</strong> every day?</div><div class="fr">Question → mets DOES devant, enlève le S</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="lesson-card"><div class="lesson-title">✏️ Entraîne-toi !</div>
    <div id="build-container"></div>
    <button class="btn" onclick="checkBuild()">Corriger ✓</button>
    <button class="btn-outline" onclick="resetBuild()">Recommencer</button>
    <div id="build-result" style="margin-top:0.8rem"></div>
  </div>
</div>

